Tags:
  - Life-Love=Prayer-Meditation-Contemplation=The Safeguarding of Prayer
By: Swami Sivananda
---
You must never forget the idea ‘I am Brahman’, the idea of the divine
presence, for even a single instant. The forgetfulness of God is a
veritable death, a suicide; it is the murder of the Âtman (âtmadroha).
And it is the greatest sin.
